Hello:



I am using/building Cantera on MS Windows platforms.  Since I am using
SunDials for numeric solvers I modified the clib project properties to
remove cvode.lib from the linker inputs.  I then had to make sure the
project dependencies were correct to get the project to link.



I have two source trees on my development computer.  One has the Cantera
1.7.0 sources and the other is current from CVS.  I develop and test
external code against the 1.7.0 source tree.  



